he_camel/camel_core/ApiMethodParserTest.java`\n\nThe new test exercises `ArgumentSubstitutionParser`/`ApiMethodParser.parse()` through supported public API behavior and covers:\n- `Class.forName(...)` for fully qualified types\n- fallback `java.lang` class loading\n- array type resolution via `Array.newInstance(...)`\n- reflective `proxyType.getMethod(...)` lookup\n\nI did not run the tests, per workflow instructions.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07ea1e3928618d31016a28545c83e48193a278347f5099a3f2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 413, "output": 1170, "cacheRead": 24064, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 25647, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781027899625, "responseId": "resp_07ea1e3928618d31016a28543c58e081939b295487628f6192"}}
